# Backrooms Muffler

- **Product:** Backrooms Muffler — liminal room-muffle VST3/AU effect
- **CMake target:** `BackroomsMuffler` | **Display name:** `Backrooms Muffler`
- **Stack:** JUCE 8 (submodule), CMake 3.22+, C++20
- **License:** AGPL-3.0 — keep source open when distributing

## Layout

- `source/dsp/BackroomsProcessor.*` — audio DSP
- `source/ui/` — Backrooms LookAndFeel and wallpaper
- `source/PluginProcessor.*` / `PluginEditor.*` — JUCE plugin shell
- `docs/DSP.md` — parameter curves; read before tuning
- `docs/BUILD.md` — build, test, Ableton install
- `docs/UI.md` — palette and asset policy

## Rules

- Do **not** use Projucer; CMake only
- No heap alloc / locks / file I/O in `processBlock`
- UI assets must be **original** — no ripped Backrooms game/film art
- APVTS param IDs: `corner`, `hall`, `depth`, `mix`, `muffle`

## Build

```powershell
cmake --preset vs2022
cmake --build --preset vs2022-release
```
